    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E92 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. This S65 V8 powerhouse remains the gold standard of the M-division, featuring a redline that screams to 8,400 RPM with visceral induction noise. This example is mechanically dialed; the rod bearings have been addressed with treated shells for peace of mind, and the throttle actuators exhibit zero latency. The DCT transmission logic has been flashed for lightning-fast engagement, paired with a subframe that is structurally flawless. Suspension geometry is optimized with EDC-tuned dampers and fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber for surgical turn-in. This is a turn-key, analog masterpiece for the purist who demands peak mechanical synergy and a pristine chassis. Zero leaks, zero codes, and a compression profile that remains within factory tolerances.",
